OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPope Francis to visit      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FCanada for indigenous      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freconciliation             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pope Francis has agreed to visit Canada
OL,6, to assist with ongoing reconciliation  
OL,7, efforts with indigenous groups, the    
OL,8, Vatican said on Wednesday.             
OL,10,FThe trip follows disturbing revelations
OL,11,Fthis spring about the indigenous       
OL,12,Fchildren who died while attending      
OL,13,Fresidential schools.                   
OL,15,FThe Catholic Church was essential in   
OL,16,Fthe schools' founding and operation.   
OL,18,FThe date of the papal visit has not yet
OL,19,Fbeen announced.                        
